reviews.text:
Vaping this after 10 days on a Goon LP, 0.35ohm, dual coil SS316. The RY4 is very nice, caramelly on the inhale, with the subtle bourbon on the exhale. I feel like the vanilla custard is there as well, but it's subtle. I don't really taste the graham cracker (althought I suppose it might be acting more as binding the flavors together) nor the toasted marshmellow.&#xD;
&#xD;
Recipe is delicious however. Agree with the KRUCIAL's review that bumping the toasted marshmallow might further improve it.
